---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="PeptideBay terms of service - usage agreement and disclaimers.">

<section class="py-12 lg:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-industrial-100 mb-4">
        <span class="text-chem-green">Terms</span> of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="text-industrial-400">
        Last updated: February 2026
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Critical Disclaimer -->
    <div class="industrial-panel border-l-4 border-l-chem-red mb-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-chem-red mb-4">
        ⚠️ CRITICAL MEDICAL DISCLAIMER
      </h2>
      <p class="text-industrial-300 leading-relaxed font-semibold">
        THE INFORMATION PROVIDED ON THIS WEBSITE IS FOR EDUCATIONAL AND RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY. IT IS NOT INTENDED AS MEDICAL ADVICE, DIAGNOSIS, OR TREATMENT.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-industrial-400 mt-4 text-sm">
        <li>• Many compounds discussed are NOT approved for human use</li>
        <li>• Always consult a qualified healthcare professional</li>
        <li>• Do not use any compound without proper medical guidance</li>
        <li>• We do NOT sell, distribute, or endorse any substances</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      
      <div class="industrial-panel">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-industrial-100 mb-4">
          1. Acceptance of Terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-industrial-300 leading-relaxed">
          By accessing PeptideBay, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use this website.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="industrial-panel">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-industrial-100 mb-4">
          2. Nature of Content
        </h2>
        <p class="text-industrial-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          PeptideBay provides informational content about research compounds, including:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-industrial-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-green">•</span>
            Peptides and research chemicals
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-green">•</span>
            Supplements and nootropics
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-green">•</span>
            Scientific research citations
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-green">•</span>
            Aggregated user experiences
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-industrial-400 mt-4 text-sm border-t border-industrial-700 pt-4">
          This content is compiled from publicly available sources and should not be considered complete or authoritative.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="industrial-panel">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-industrial-100 mb-4">
          3. No Medical Advice
        </h2>
        <p class="text-industrial-300 leading-relaxed">
          PeptideBay does not provide medical advice. The content is for informational purposes only. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking it because of something you have read on this website.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="industrial-panel">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-industrial-100 mb-4">
          4. Limitation of Liability
        </h2>
        <p class="text-industrial-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          To the fullest extent permitted by law:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-industrial-400">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-red mt-1">•</span>
            <span>We make NO WARRANTIES about the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of information</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-red mt-1">•</span>
            <span>We are NOT liable for any actions taken based on website content</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-red mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Use of any information is at your OWN RISK</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-red mt-1">•</span>
            <span>We are NOT responsible for third-party links or content</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="industrial-panel">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-industrial-100 mb-4">
          5. User Conduct
        </h2>
        <p class="text-industrial-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          By using this website, you agree NOT to:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-industrial-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-amber">•</span>
            Use the information for illegal purposes
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-amber">•</span>
            Attempt to hack, scrape excessively, or disrupt the service
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-chem-amber">•</span>
            Misrepresent the source of information
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="industrial-panel">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-industrial-100 mb-4">
          6. Intellectual Property
        </h2>
        <p class="text-industrial-300 leading-relaxed">
          Website design, code, and original content are © PeptideBay. Research citations and external content remain property of their respective owners.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="industrial-panel">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-industrial-100 mb-4">
          7. Changes to Terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-industrial-300 leading-relaxed">
          We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use constitutes acceptance of changes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="industrial-panel">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-industrial-100 mb-4">
          8. Contact
        </h2>
        <p class="text-industrial-300 leading-relaxed">
          For questions about these terms:
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:legal@peptidebay.shop" class="inline-block mt-4 btn-lab">
          legal@peptidebay.shop
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Final Warning -->
    <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-industrial-900/50 border border-industrial-700 text-center">
      <p class="font-heading text-chem-green text-lg mb-2">
        Remember: Research Responsibly
      </p>
      <p class="text-industrial-400 text-sm">
        This website is for educational purposes only. Always consult healthcare professionals before making any decisions about compounds or supplements.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
